{"tid":2514302,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"聲援抗爭遭阻撓 校方懶理  留英港生蒐罪證 反擊小粉紅霸權","createTime":"2021-05-03T07:24:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T07:31:12.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b6f5d89b96c176eecf0a0c98356922a3782d28b3","tid":2514302,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T07:24:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210503/INAMXMRDC5FBBHHF3NA457YBZE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210503%2FINAMXMRDC5FBBHHF3NA457YBZE%2F&d=xOzWlad5M6duuHBPObmdODcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=e6404441\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210503%2FINAMXMRDC5FBBHHF3NA457YBZE%2F&h=68618d08\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210503/INAMXMRDC5FBBHHF3NA457YBZE/</a><br />\n<br />\n聲援抗爭遭阻撓 校方懶理 <br />\n留英港生蒐罪證 反擊小粉紅霸權<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】英國大學一向崇尚言論自由，惟英國政府近年點名批評大學過份依賴收取中國留學生的高額學費，令校園內的自由受到侵蝕。有香港留學生表示，前年反修例運動期間在校園舉辦聲援香港活動時，不但遭校方阻撓，即使成功申請，亦遭有中共背景的校內組織包圍騷擾甚至強搶文宣，迫使他們中止活動。有香港留學生組織自發收集更多同類個案，以撰寫報告向政府進一步反映情況，望能守護校園內的言論自由。<br />\n<br />\n特約記者譚志輝英國報道<br />\n<br />\n今年將本科畢業的Jamie（化名），就讀倫敦市內一所頂級大學，反修例運動期間，原擬與數位同樣來自香港的留學生成立關注香港問題的學生組織，卻被大學學生會拒絕，「他們沒具體說甚麼原因，有人說可能我們倡議的太敏感，但事實是校內有各個不同政治取態鮮明的學生組織，為何獨獨針對香港議題？」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Ezh6hNwTK_OeTCHCrDSHwt0yKGM=/510x309/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/S6CVIFMBIFDSTI55KWQTTTK3OI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FEzh6hNwTK_OeTCHCrDSHwt0yKGM%3D%2F510x309%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FS6CVIFMBIFDSTI55KWQTTTK3OI.jpg&h=04d9a91b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■Jamie（左）和Kitty（右）辦聲援港人活動時遭中國學生騷擾，嘆中共滲透令英國校園自由受損。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n糾眾踩場 獲大使館撐腰<br />\n<br />\n無法成立學生組織，Jamie惟有與現有學生組織合作，「剛好國際特赦組織的校內分部當年工作的主題是保障人權和示威權，我們就與他們商討合作就香港議題發聲。」最終她們以國際特赦組織名義，向校方申請一連兩日在學生中心外舉辦香港示威與警暴的展覽。<br />\n<br />\n展覽前年11月底首日展出時，。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n其後數名中國學生到場，開始用普通話指罵她們是港獨分子發放假新聞，指她們。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n最終校園保安要求Jamie腰斬展覽，原。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n英議員：學術自由遭侵蝕<br />\n<br />\n在倫敦一所羅素集團名校就讀的Kitty（化名）亦有類似遭遇，她前年10月1日在校內與數位港人學生即興發起Stand With HK集會，當時出席者包括十數位香港和本地學生，各人手持自製文宣及高叫支持香港的口號，惟未幾即有中國學生到場，用普通話指罵他們是「曱甴」、「漢奸」等，「突然有個臉容十分凶悍的中國學生閃出到我身前，瞪着我的時序表，之後對我怒目相向，發難一手扯下我的文宣丟在地上。」保安員即時將涉事人帶走，並要求Kitty等人先行離去，Kitty一夥擔心情況會失控，只好屈服。<br />\n<br />\n由執政保守黨資助的智庫ONWARD去年發表研究報告，指英國大學過份依賴來自中。。。。。。。英國學術界在敏感議題上噤聲，並直言「英國的學術自由遭到侵蝕。」<br />\n<br />\n有見及此，香港留學生組織「香港思源」去年起收集大學生在校園發表有。。。。<br />\n<br />\nBasil強調參與者身份絕對保密，資料使用後會銷毀，希望有類似Jamie和Kitty遭遇的學生，無論是否來自香港，都可聯絡他們並提供資料。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/T6taAkRY1Eaa7SpGAtWXho4pQAA=/510x713/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/U3ICIBZHPZBGVDZWEAPYLNBLGU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FT6taAkRY1Eaa7SpGAtWXho4pQAA%3D%2F510x713%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FU3ICIBZHPZBGVDZWEAPYLNBLGU.jpg&h=e074ebf8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■英國議員董勤達指中共透過威嚇手段迫使英國院校噤聲。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/5Uc0ObqWKw07JkKiLRXqo92Vu9Y=/510x339/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MQKH3AYNTFEU3AROBFF5VL2T3U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F5Uc0ObqWKw07JkKiLRXqo92Vu9Y%3D%2F510x339%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMQKH3AYNTFEU3AROBFF5VL2T3U.jpg&h=e419a3c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【小粉紅經常踩場】■2019年起在英港人多次舉辦集會聲援香港，屢有當地中國移民及留學生到場指罵及揮舞五星旗。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/APNAs5tcAbFGiFc4rZ1E8ef9gtg=/510x339/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3JKMO4JQ55DRRCO4ZWXBJ2IGGI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FAPNAs5tcAbFGiFc4rZ1E8ef9gtg%3D%2F510x339%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3JKMO4JQ55DRRCO4ZWXBJ2IGGI.jpg&h=c59ef059&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【小粉紅經常踩場】<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/U9QxvlhF6GweScosHy3SaNLIHns=/510x339/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZJPKPNIPJVGMXBCGNCBHDY4QRA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FU9QxvlhF6GweScosHy3SaNLIHns%3D%2F510x339%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZJPKPNIPJVGMXBCGNCBHDY4QRA.jpg&h=84eb0021&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【小粉紅經常踩場】<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/lEh2nnbAbkYUM9s2ew-QOrHq8MM=/510x267/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/HOSVBOA63JGF5P75DHGTEVAL6E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FlEh2nnbAbkYUM9s2ew-QOrHq8MM%3D%2F510x267%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FHOSVBOA63JGF5P75DHGTEVAL6E.jpg&h=f5dc2c84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【小粉紅經常踩場】"},{"pid":"d1cb89b1d3a6862fcc8166148573d923802a8c20","tid":2514302,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T07:28:19.000Z","msg":"wtf is 本科"},{"pid":"b3d55f7ea225e69667b84e9286d8073f51589dda","tid":2514302,"uid":327169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T07:31:12.000Z","msg":"邊個支那國學生敢搞事，即刻同移民部講，同學校講有L用咩"}]}